OL,3,CMan says life 'ruined' after wife and
OL,4,Cson killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,FHill, of Wheata Road in Sheffield,
OL,7,Ffled the scene and was on the run for
OL,8,Ftwo days before being arrested. He
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to causing death by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving on the first day of
OL,11,Fhis trial at Derby Crown Court and was
OL,12,Fjailed for 13 years.
OL,14,FMrs Boyack's husband Billy and their
OL,15,Fother son Alex witnessed the crash as
OL,16,Fthey travelled in the vehicle behind.
OL,18,FMr Boyack said: "I am still constantly
OL,19,Fhaving the most horrific and soul
OL,20,Fsickening flashbacks to the collision
OL,21,Fwhich continue to be crippling for me."
