OL,6,FHe said the deaths of his wife and son
OL,7,Fhad left a hole in their community in
OL,8,FSouth Shields.
OL,10,F"Angela was a caring, loving wife and
OL,11,Ffriend to me and loving mother to both
OL,12,FAlex and Stephen," he said.
OL,14,F"Losing my wife Angela and my son
OL,15,FStephen has ruined my life in every
OL,16,Fsense of the word and meaning.
