OL,3,CMan says life 'ruined' after wife and
OL,4,Cson killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,F"Angela was everything to me. In
OL,7,Flosing her I have realised what it was
OL,8,Fthat she did for me and for us as a
OL,9,Ffamily ` all the little things that
OL,10,Fdon't get done now because they were
OL,11,Fnot something I had to think about.
OL,13,F"The house is not the same, everything
OL,14,Fis a constant and unbearably painful
OL,15,Freminder of her ` everywhere I go I
OL,16,Fsee her and cannot stop thinking about
OL,17,Fthe loss and pain that this has
OL,18,Fcaused."
