OL,6,FAlex Boyack said of his brother:
OL,7,F"Stephen was not just my younger
OL,8,Fbrother, he was my best friend. We
OL,9,Fwere like a double act, we would play
OL,10,Fconsole games together, go play pool
OL,11,Fwith friends together, go out and
OL,12,Fsocialise together. We got on so well,
OL,13,Fwe would know what each other was
OL,14,Fthinking at times.
