OL,3,CMan says life 'ruined' after wife and
OL,4,Cson killed in hit-and-run
OL,6,F"My biggest fear has always been of
OL,7,Flosing Stephen. I even had dreams
OL,8,Fbefore the collision that Stephen
OL,9,Fwould one day die and I would be on my
OL,10,Fown. I'd wake up in a panic thinking
OL,11,Fit was real then would get relief when
OL,12,FI'd wake to find it wasn't. Sadly now
OL,13,FI wake up and never get that relief
OL,14,Fanymore because this is real and it's
OL,15,Fa living nightmare."
OL,17,FMr Boyack said there were no words to
OL,18,Fdescribe his "disgust and contempt"
OL,19,Ffor Hill.
